text: Morning Rob... How are you doing?
Hey Jon, been an exhausting weekend. Not sure what virus I do have but it sure knocked it out of me over the weekend
I keep meaning to respond to your previous message, but I ran out of steam Friday and have just been taking it easy trying to relax

Hey Rob, No probs at all. Take it easy!
I seem to have had the mild version - sore throat for two weeks + a fever + serious drowsiness for a day. Now totally recovered - fingers crossed. I was so worried I'd maybe offended you with my stream of consciousness. Life is totally unreal rn. Finally making some good progress w projections and roto. Trying to have a routine every day and give a solid 8hrs + to each. Stay safe & get better!
